Description:
An Inspired High Rise Docklands Sensation within Minutes to South Wharf
With breathtaking views of the renowned Yarra’s Edge marina and Melbourne CBD, this immaculate owner occupied residence is an outstanding opportunity for the most fastidious of buyers.
With a spacious central living zone this apartment promotes an expansive lounge and dining area, an exquisite kitchen with feature island bench, clever storage plus stainless steel Miele appliances including a dishwasher and gas cook top. All of this is beautifully framed by floor to ceiling windows and an undercover balcony, capturing the marvellous views of the marina, Southbank and beyond.
The sizeable master suite is completed with a walk-in robe and deluxe ensuite, while a 2nd bedroom with built-in robe, third bedroom/home office, impressive central bathroom, and separate laundry are further highlights. Other extras include ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces. Residents have access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
For those who want to live the amazing Docklands lifestyle, this one is for you. Hitting lively South Wharf restaurants will become part of your weekend routine, with Bangpop, The General Assembly, and Akachochin Japanese restaurant accessible within a few minutes’ walk, not to mention premium shopping within South Wharf DFO. You’re also not far from Crown Entertainment Complex, Capital City Trail, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
ABSOLUTE WATERFRONT LIVING!!
On offer is this superb three bedroom apartment high on the 28th floor and directly facing the water
Located in the luxurious 'Convesso', this 5 –star building has set the bench-mark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The views from this beautiful apartment could not be better as you peer from your living room or main bedroom across the water to NewQuay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to the Bolte Bridge. "Beautiful by day, Fantastic by Night."
This stylish apartment comprises of three spacious bedrooms, a designer kitchen, stone bench tops, refrigerator and an abundance of cupboard space, living room with amazing water views, a wide balcony perfect for entertaining or relaxing, two boutique hotel style bathrooms, ducted air conditioning and heating, two secure undercover car spaces and a storage cage.
In addition, the amenities in this luxurious building includes are a 24 hour concierge, residents lounge, Business Centre & Board Room, Cinema (within the Concavo building), North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities, 25 metre pool, spa and sauna, gymnasium and treatment room.
Don't miss a fantastic opportunity to secure this apartment right by the waterside!

Description:
Picturesque at Palladio
Like the prow of a ship, The Palladio certainly grabs your attention. Named after Italian architect, Andrea Palladio, the residential complex is a much sought after in New Quay.
This fantastic level 17, two bedroom apartment has the most spectacular water views across the harbour expanse and towards Port Phillip bay.
Large kitchen with peninsula bench provides great space for preparing and cooking meals.
Open plan dining and living area with floor to ceiling windows adjoins a south facing balcony.
Large main bedroom with ensuite, walk through robe, study nook and private balcony.
Second bedroom with with built in robes
Fully tiled shared central bathroom and European style laundry
Other features include
Reverse cycle split system heating and cooling
Under cover secure car space
Storage cage
Complex facilities include
Swimming pool, gymnasium, Communal BBQ area and function room.
Onsite manager
Remote garage entrance
Free tram zoned, close to Southern Cross Station and easy access with the freeway system.
A short stroll to the revamped The District Docklands shopping, Costco, O’Brien House Ice Skating and the “Ron Barassi Snr” recreational park nearby.
New cinemas and Woolworths under construction for opening early 2019
Fully furnished and ready to go. Perfect for the investor or to move in.
Call Eugene to arrange an inspection now.

Description:
Central Docklands - Enjoy Harbourside Living
Situated centrally in the heart of Docklands, Serrata is an impressive boutique residential complex located on Bourke Street and close to Victoria Green. This apartment represents the essence of city living with plenty of commerce, retail, and cultural offerings all within easy access to the CBD.
This modern 1 bedroom apartment has an excellent sized bedroom with built in wardrobes. Spacious open plan designed living room with access to a wide balcony and floor to ceiling windows. An open plan kitchen meals area featuring stainless appliances including cook top, wall oven and dishwasher. Completing the apartment is a large bathroom clear glass shower - a size not commonly found in the typical apartment.
Serrata has also achieved a 4 Star Green Star Multi-Unit Residential Design rating. Coming home to Serrata after a long day will be a welcoming way to relax, recharge and enter into a sense of calm. Here is your chance to secure a practical home for occupancy or investment in a cosmopolitan suburb.
Contact us today to book a private inspection.

Description:
Come for the Space and Style, Stay for the Amazing Views!
An exceptional harmony of sophisticated contemporary elegance and fabulous space, this two bedroom, two bathroom residence in Tower 3 of Yarra’s Edge has the magnificent CBD and marina as your daily backdrop!
This flawless abode sits high on the 16th floor and delivers superb detail from stone surfaces, floor-to-ceiling windows, and breathtaking uninterrupted views. The expansive central living zone has designated lounge and dining spaces, with this airy hub further oozing out to the full-length North/East facing balcony which displays some of the most spectacular skyline views in all of the Docklands.
A dazzling kitchen is ideal for home gourmands with a long breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom is an excellent size and includes dual mirrored BIRs and a double vanity ensuite, meanwhile the spacious 2nd bedroom with BIRs is a few steps to the striking central bathroom. Both bedrooms also have balcony access. Also enjoy a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, 2 car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The superb Yarra’s Edge precinct sits right on the banks of the iconic river and is a dream spot for owner-occupiers looking to make the Docklands change. You’re close to an array of brilliant attractions in the South Wharf area which is alive on Friday and Saturday nights, while nearby DFO Shopping, Capital City Trail, Crown Casino, public transport, and Victoria Harbour precinct via Webb Bridge is easily accessed.

Description:
FABULOUS DOCKLANDS HOME WITH STUNNING VIEWS
Overlooking Victoria Harbour on the 21st floor of the Boyd Complex is this magnificent, light filled, corner apartment showcasing breathtaking views with an intelligent floor plan. Featuring floorboards throughout the living zones, and offering an open-plan living, dining, and kitchen, this contemporary 3 bedroom home is built for entertaining.
The entrance hall flows into the living zone and out onto the balcony, which presents an awe-inspiring panorama of Victoria Harbour out to Port Philip Bay – perfect for enjoying a cold drink after a long day.
The beautifully appointed kitchen features stone-bench tops, stainless steel Miele appliances, integrated fridge, and plenty of storage in the stylish cupboards. Imagine cooking up a storm in your new kitchen whilst taking in the dazzling display of the Iconic Melbourne Star.
The master bedroom is generous in size for apartment living, featuring sensational views to the north, a walk-in-robe, and a stylish ensuite with a clean, modern finish. The second bedroom is also generous in size, with a large floor to ceiling wardrobe, and also presents great views to the north of the Melbourne Star and Mount Macedon. The third bedroom is reasonably sized, with a built in robe, and works perfectly as a guest room, child's room or study.
Rounding out this chic Docklands home is a central bathroom, complete with separate shower and bath, as well as a powder room, and laundry room. Central heating & cooling, 2 secure side by side car spaces, and secure swipe & intercom entry complete this smart inner city pad.
Including use of the swimming pool, gymnasium, and function rooms, this is resort style living 365 days a year. Conveniently located in the free tram zone, and in the North Melbourne Primary School & University High School zones, this home would suit investors and families alike. And with Etihad Stadium, a world class shopping precinct, and an array of waterside restaurants & bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

On offer is this immaculate one bedroom unit nestled nicely on the 9th floor of the Aqui Promenade building. This brilliant north west facing home delivers stylishly contemporary interiors and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light. The art of stylish, light-filled and sophisticated Docklands living is on display here with this north-facing two bedroom apartment, which is part of the stunning The Quays complex and offers buyers one of the best opportunities in the NewQuay precinct.
Experience some of the best high rise living from the 25th floor, with the wonderful northern orientation and breathtaking CBD views to the east adding to the property’s appeal. Generous space for lounge and dining is matched by a delightful stone kitchen which is complete with stainless steel Miele appliances and a colourful glass splashback.
The sensational balcony exhibits beautiful views to the north as well as the iconic city, with both bedrooms boasting access to the balcony including the main bedroom which features ample built-in robe storage. Further embrace the dazzling bathroom with laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage and secure car space.

Description:
The Pinnacle of Docklands Luxury in Yarra’s Edge
An absolutely astounding combination of brilliant internal space, picturesque views, and refined designer touches that add a true elegance to your daily life, this fully renovated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom apartment is sure to have passionate Docklands buyers in a frenzy.
The sheer size of the central lounge and dining zone will be enough to convince you of this property’s special appeal, with this main hub enjoying beautiful Spanish tiling underfoot and marvelous views of the Yarra River and CBD. Included in this everyday hub is the gourmet stone kitchen which overlooks the living and dining zone while promising a large, stone island bench, Miele Oven and cooktop, oversized dishwasher, soft close drawers and superior quality fixtures and fittings.
Three bedrooms in total puts this apartment in rarefied air, with each bedroom boasting a phenomenal amount of space and wool carpets, including the master retreat which comes with custom joinery and gorgeous ensuite with sophisticated charm. The second bedroom features a generous walk-in robe, third bedroom with BIR’s and both are just steps to the stylish main bathroom.
The unforgettable balcony has a north-west orientation and will be your home for summer relaxing over meals and wines, while further enjoy a powder room, huge separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Your Friday nights and weekends will be taken care of thanks to the close proximity to the lively South Wharf Promenade which has a multitude of amazing eateries and bars including Bangpop, Munich Brauhaus, The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard just to name a few. You’re also near Crown Casino with world class restaurants and transport including Southern Cross Station and trams on Spencer Street and Whiteman Street.

Description:
Luxury penthouse living with awe-inspiring views
High on the 30th floor of the luxury Award Winning Forge complex, this 3 BR + study penthouse dazzles with high end finishes and uninterrupted CBD and river views. Complete with designer Cosh furniture and boasting a northern orientation, you'll never tire of the stunning vistas, bright places to lounge, dine, and sleep, and superb building facilities.
- Spacious lounge and dining boasts amazing light & astonishing CBD/river vistas
- Generous winter garden can be accessed via central living and master bedroom
- Gleaming stone kitchen with quality Smeg appliances, dedicated study room
- Master bedroom with ample BIRs and gorgeous ensuite, chic rain shower bathroom
- Storage cage, 2 car spaces, access to gym, pool, kitchen/dining, and cinema

Description:
North-facing living with a designer Docklands edge
Embrace the northern orientation with light-filled and stunningly immaculate interiors of this 8th floor two bedroom Quays apartment, which offers a Docklands lifestyle like no other in the ever popular NewQuay precinct.
You’re stepping right into the action as you walk through the front door and find yourself in the fantastic meals and kitchen area, with the structured cooking space enjoying a wonderful stone benchtop, mirrored splashback and stainless steel Miele appliances.
A few steps more and you can relax in the generous lounge, which has excellent natural light filling the space and entry to the sizeable balcony which runs the full length of the apartment. It is here where you can marvel at the brilliant views to the north and east. Further enjoy a main bedroom with built-in robes, both bedrooms with balcony access, impressive bathroom, European laundry, timber floors, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and secure car space.
The world class facilities of the Quays complex is what makes this one of the most sought-after buildings in the Docklands. Enjoy a Health Club with pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Resident’s Club with library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room, cinema lounge and a rooftop garden with BBQ, dining facilities and the only tennis court in the Docklands.
You can walk to fantastic restaurants including Steakhouse 66, Bhoj Restaurant, Woolshed and Mama Rumaan. You’re also in close proximity to the new The District Docklands with fabulous shops, cinema coming soon, eateries, Etihad Stadium and trams in all directions.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
Perfect parkland position
Stylish in design, this two bedroom apartment offers City lifestyle at its best. Located centrally in the Victoria Harbour precinct and staged in front row to the beautiful Docklands Parkland. Features a spacious open plan living and dining area absorbing parkland,and CBD views, a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and stainless steel appliances. A large main bedroom with built in robes and en-suite and a large second bedroom with adjoining bathroom including deep relaxing bath and separate laundry are offered to the discerning buyer. The apartment also includes reverse cycle air conditioning and an undercover car space. Combine the pleasures of this elegant and functional floor plan with the delights and benefits of the perfect location. For further details and inspections

Description:
Marina and City Views in Arkley Lifestyle
The lifestyle that you will experience while residing on the 16th floor of one of New Quay's most keenly sought after complexes, The Arkley is second to none. A sea of lights extending to the horizon, Melbourne's Star Observation Wheel and the shimmering Marina create a fairytale-like background to the beautifully bright 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment's interior.
A balcony flowing off the living and dining room expands the space for relaxing and entertaining outdoors. Open-planned to the living room is a chic kitchen. Each of the bedrooms is fitted with built-in robes while a second balcony leads off the main bedroom. A powder room sits opposite the bathroom, which is appointed with a bath and separate shower. Completing the features are 1 car space and a European laundry.
Leisure facilities include a pool, golf net, function room and gym. The location is like no other with transport and dining-out venues at the door and the CBD within walking distance.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 for an exclusive viewing.

Description:
UNDER OFFER - Incredible Harbour, CBD And Stadium Views!
With a floorplan that maximizes space and a balcony that promises incredible views of Victoria Harbour, the city, and Etihad Stadium, this classy two bedroom corner apartment shines in the popular NewQuay precinct.
The coveted ‘Harbour 1’ complex is the setting for this 20th floor property, which excels thanks to bright full windows, stone surfaces, and a stunning open layout. Spend day and night in the relaxed lounge and dining zone, while summers nights will have you utilising the large covered balcony with views to the south and west.
Both bedrooms have the same great space and built-in robes, meanwhile the quality bathroom comes with a European laundry and the gleaming kitchen is functional for easy breakfasts, lunches, and dinners. Other extras include central heating and cooling, intercom entry, storage cage, secure car space, and access to a library lounge, media room, and gym.
Moments to The District Docklands, restaurants including Medici Docklands, Fish Bar, and Achelya Restaurant, IGA X-press supermarket, Etihad Stadium, and trams to Bundoora RMIT and the CBD.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing
